<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>College Dost - FAQs</title>
    <!-- Google Fonts for a sleek modern look -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/FAQ.css">
</head>
<body>
    
    <div id="main">
        <!-- Main Fixed Header -->
        <div id="header">
            <div class="logo">College Dost</div>     
            <div class="FAQ1"><h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1></div>
            <div class="box">
                <a href="/" class="btn-home">Home</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Fake Header spacer for fixed navbar -->
        <div id="fakeheader"></div>

        <!-- FAQ Content Wrapper -->
        <div class="faq-container">
            
            <!-- FAQ Section 1 -->
            <div class="faq-section animate-box">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">1. What is College Dost? <span class="arrow"></span></button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>College Dost is a platform connecting juniors with mentors and alumni for guidance.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">2. Who can become a mentor? <span class="arrow"></span></button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Mentors are selected by the admin based on their experience and academic/professional background.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">3. Is chat anonymous? <span class="arrow"></span></button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes, anonymous chat is available for sensitive discussions.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">4. Is the platform free? <span class="arrow"></span></button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes, it is completely free for students.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">5. How can I contact mentors? <span class="arrow"></span></button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>You can connect through the chat feature seamlessly.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">6. Do I need to create an account to use College Dost? <span class="arrow"></span></button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes, users need to register and log in to access features like chat, roadmap, and alumni content.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">7. Can juniors directly message mentors? <span class="arrow"></span></button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes, juniors can connect with mentors through the chat system once logged in.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">8. What is the roadmap feature? <span class="arrow"></span></button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>The roadmap provides a semester-wise guide to help students learn skills and technologies step by step.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- FAQ Section 2 -->
            <div class="faq-section animate-box">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">9. Can I become a mentor in the future? <span class="arrow"></span></button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes, students can apply, and mentors are selected by the admin based on performance and experience.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">10. Is my personal data safe? <span class="arrow"></span></button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes, we ensure that your personal data is stored securely and not shared with unauthorized users.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">11. What should I do if I face any issue on the platform? <span class="arrow"></span></button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>You can contact support through the Contact section available on the website.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">12. Can mentors post updates or announcements? <span class="arrow"></span></button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes, mentors can share important updates, tips, and guidance through the announcement section.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">13. Is this platform only for one college? <span class="arrow"></span></button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Currently, it is designed for our college, but it can be expanded in the future.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">14. Can I use College Dost on mobile devices? <span class="arrow"></span></button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes, the platform is responsive and works on both desktop and mobile browsers.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">15. What is the purpose of anonymous chat? <span class="arrow"></span></button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Anonymous chat allows users to ask sensitive or personal questions without revealing their identity.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Script connection -->
    <script src="/js/FAQ.js"></script>
</body>
</html>